# Dialog Primary Action Motion

When adding or updating a dialog, the primary action button should use the same press-scale interaction used elsewhere in the planner UI.

Use this class on primary dialog actions:

```tsx
className="active:scale-[0.97] ease-out will-change-transform motion-reduce:transition-none motion-reduce:active:scale-100"
```

Apply this to the main confirm/submit/copy/save action in dialogs. Secondary actions like Cancel, Close, or destructive confirmation buttons should only use this pattern when the surrounding UI already does.
